svg.desc: Native R DLNM package analysis using: • dlnm package by Gasparrini • crossbasis() function for cross-basis creation • crosspred() function for predictions • plot.crosspred() for native DLNM plots • Temperature-CD4 distributed lag non-linear model • R² = 0.036, N = 1283 observations
